### Build Order
Follow this sequence (each step depends on prior):
1. Database schema (Prisma) + seed data
2. Authentication (login, JWT, middleware)
3. Admin console (user CRUD, roles)
4. Source CRUD + Source List page
5. Clause CRUD + inline table
6. Task Template CRUD + per-clause cards
7. Source Creation Wizard (4-step)
8. Source Detail page
9. Task generation cron job
10. Task Tracker + Task Detail
11. Review Queue
12. Reminder/Overdue/Escalation cron jobs
13. Audit log system
14. Ownership model (dept queue, self-assign)
15. Entity & Group monitoring
16. Dashboard
17. Configurable Reports
18. AI source parsing
19. AI Chat
20. Slack integration
